            "answer": "<p>We begin with grounding breathwork and a live crystal sound bath. As the bowls play, most people notice something shift — the body softens, the mind quiets. </p><p>From there, I guide you into a deeply relaxed state where your higher self leads. Every session is different because every soul is different</p><p> People leave feeling grounded, clear, and like themselves again — sometimes more than they ever have.</p>"
          }
