          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do I need any experience or preparation?",
            "answer": "<p>None at all. These sessions are for everyone — the deeply spiritual and the quietly curious alike. </p><p>You don't need the right words or the right mindset. Just show up. Your higher self takes it from there.</p>"
          }
