          "settings": {
            "question": "Are sessions available online or only in person?",
            "answer": "<p>Both. Sessions are available in person in San Pancho, Mexico or Austin, Texas and also online so you can experience this from wherever you are. The depth of the work translates fully — location doesn't limit what's possible.</p>"
